message.content: "You're durned foolin', mister," said the man called Roper Smith. "We've got five rifles among us and a few six-shooters. But most of us ain't eddicated in shootin'. It'd be a massacre, yessir." "If you'll take a chance on getting your gold to the bank, then we'll abide by what we said at the meeting," said Dan. "We'll watch the stage out of reach."
